### Stage 2: AI Art Studio (Core Feature)
- **Scope:** Dedicated "Art Studio" interface with 4-step AI image generation process
- **User Flow:** Magic wand customization → Describe image → Style selection → AI generation → Refinement → Apply
- **Technical:** Gemini API integration, image management system, sophisticated UX flows  
